  "closed_at": "2016-07-14T07:15:48Z",
  "body": "同样的代码在5.1下可以全屏，Miui 4.4.4下高度只能占到父容器的4/5左右。\nnative端render、renderByUrl都试过，效果一样。\njs端也设置了ready: function () {\n            this.ctHeight = this.$getConfig().env.deviceHeight;\n            console.log(\"screenHeight:\" + this.ctHeight);\n        }\nmWXSDKInstance.renderByUrl(TAG, \"http://192.168.137.1:8080/dist/index.js\", null, null, -1, -1, WXRenderStrategy.APPEND_ASYNC);\n\nweex版本：compile 'com.taobao.android:weex_sdk:0.5.1@aar'\n"
